Quick howto:

1/ install jbake 2.2.1 (http://jbake.org)
2/ build the site : mvn package -> it creates the content in target/output
3/ to preview the site run : "jbake --server" in the target directory
4/ open browser to localhost:8820

for instance with bash:

% cd juzu.github.com
% mvn package
% ...
% cd target
% jbake --server

